              "value": "=Help me create a rhyming picture book called \"A Child’s First Book on {{ $('Set Book Topic').item.json.topic }}\", introducing the concept of {{ $('Set Book Topic').item.json.topic }} in a simple, magical way children can understand.\n\nThe book should be written in rhyming couplets — 2 lines per page. \n\nThink Dr. Seuss meets {{ $json.author }}, with the cozy feel of a vintage Golden Book.\nWords should be simple modern day words.\n\nThe book should end with a closing page that simply says:\n\"THE END\"",
